<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Pesanan Berhasil</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-cover bg-center min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center font-sans" style="background-image: url('/assets/images/background.jpg');">

  <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-gray-500 px-10 py-12 max-w-xl text-center">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Terima Kasih!</h1>

    <img src="/assets/images/successful character.svg" alt="Success" class="mx-auto w-32 h-32 mb-6" />

    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 mb-1">Pesanan Anda untuk <strong><%= produk.nama %></strong> telah berhasil.</p>
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 mb-6">File akan segera diunduh secara otomatis. Jika tidak, klik tombol di bawah ini.</p>

    <a href="/uploads/<%= produk.fileZip %>" download class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-blue-700 transition text-sm font-semibold">
  DownloadÂ File
</a>
  </div>

  <script>
  window.onload = function () {
    const link = document.createElement('a');
    link.href = "/uploads/<%= produk.fileZip %>";
    link.setAttribute('download', '');
    document.body.appendChild(link);
    link.click();
    document.body.removeChild(link);
  };
</script>

</body>
</html>